title: Ps Vita vhbl 2.12
description:
The new latest version of vhbl has now been released for the ps vita running

the latest software 2.12. but in order to get this custom homebrew software running

on your vita you must have already bought the game gamocracy : legend of robot from

the marketplace if you haven't you will be unable to get it since it has been taken

down from the psn marketplace. Although i have included in the rar file my pgame

folder which contains the game gamocracy: legend of robot it will not run if you

dont have the license which you get once you buy the game but it could be possible to

bypass that security feature or once the game gets put back on the psn store buy it

but dont install it instead install my copy since the new one will have patches to

prevent the exploit and hope to god it works this is just a theory but i hope we can

get everyone that desires to run these custom homebrews on their vita gets it.
